      <title>特朗普媒体股价在辩论后因禁售期即将到期而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/trump-media-shares-slide-after-debate-as-lockup-expiry-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三早盘，在唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 与总统竞选对手卡马拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 进行辩论后，其社交媒体公司的股价大跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/trump-media-shares-slide-after-debate-as-lockup-expiry-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 12:24:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国辩论后，特朗普交易进一步减少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/trump-trades-are-being-dialed-back-even-more-after-the-us-debate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[市场观察人士认为昨晚的辩论提高了卡马拉·哈里斯获胜的前景，因此交易员进一步平仓唐纳德·特朗普入主白宫的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/trump-trades-are-being-dialed-back-even-more-after-the-us-debate</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 12:09:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党贵族曼德尔森未能申报其共同创立的公关公司的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/labour-peer-mandelson-fails-to-declare-large-stake-in-pr-firm-he-co-founded</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国工党大佬彼得·曼德尔森不得不纠正有关他拥有一家政治咨询公司股份的公开记录，此前他声称自己已将该公司全部出售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/labour-peer-mandelson-fails-to-declare-large-stake-in-pr-firm-he-co-founded</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 12:00:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称他不愿意与哈里斯再次进行辩论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/trump-says-he-s-not-inclined-toward-another-debate-with-harris</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普最初建议在周二的论坛上增加几场对决作为补充，但他表示，自己不愿意与卡马拉·哈里斯再进行一次辩论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/trump-says-he-s-not-inclined-toward-another-debate-with-harris</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 11:56:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯指挥官称对乌克兰入侵的反击已开始</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/russian-commander-says-counterattack-to-ukraine-incursion-starts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫斯科军队声称已开始进攻，驱逐乌克兰在俄罗斯库尔斯克地区的军队，这是自基辅入侵五周多以来他们首次采取重大行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/russian-commander-says-counterattack-to-ukraine-incursion-starts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 10:55:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>裕信银行对德国商业银行的举动令德国措手不及</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/german-government-wrong-footed-by-unicredit-move-on-commerzbank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利联合信贷银行 (UniCredit SpA) 对德国商业银行 (Commerzbank AG) 的惊人举动令德国政府措手不及，并使德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨 (Olaf Scholz) 陷入困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/german-government-wrong-footed-by-unicredit-move-on-commerzbank</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 10:44:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国称 5 亿英镑塔塔交易尽管裁员但仍能帮助员工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/uk-to-confirm-500m-support-package-for-tata-steel-s-port-talbot</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府确认向塔塔钢铁公司位于塔尔伯特港的工厂提供 5 亿英镑（6.55 亿美元）的支持计划，这是对工党振兴英国工业承诺的首批重大考验之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/uk-to-confirm-500m-support-package-for-tata-steel-s-port-talbot</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 08:36:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>两名以色列士兵在加沙直升机坠毁事件中丧生</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-helicopter-crash-in-southern-gaza</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两名以色列士兵昨晚在加沙地带上空因一架直升机坠毁而丧生，当时他们正执行将一名受伤士兵转移到医院的任务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-helicopter-crash-in-southern-gaza</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 08:19:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非民主联盟称教育法案对联盟构成威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/south-africa-s-da-says-education-bill-poses-threat-to-coalition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非第二大政党警告称，总统西里尔·拉马福萨批准修改教育立法的计划对该国联合政府构成威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/south-africa-s-da-says-education-bill-poses-threat-to-coalition</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 08:16:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡马拉·哈里斯如何诱使特朗普按照她的意愿展开辩论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-09-11/harris-bet-debate-on-baiting-trump-on-abortion-project-2025-it-mostly-worked</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普让自己分心，没有努力定义哈里斯，而她则强调她的核心论点，即前总统不适合担任这份工作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-09-11/harris-bet-debate-on-baiting-trump-on-abortion-project-2025-it-mostly-worked</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 05:58:26 GMT</pubDate>
